#!/bin/bash

cat << 'EOF'
# Neovim IDE Keybinds (Leader = Space)

## File Navigation
- Ctrl+p       - Find files
- <leader>ff   - Find files (alt)
- <leader>fg   - Live grep search
- <leader>fG   - Advanced grep with args
- <leader>fb   - Find buffers
- <leader>fh   - Help tags
- <leader>fr   - Recent files
- Ctrl+n       - Oil file browser
- <leader>-    - Open parent directory

## Symbol Navigation
- gd           - Go to definition
- gD           - Go to declaration
- gi           - Go to implementation
- gt           - Go to type definition
- gr           - Find references
- <leader>fs   - Document symbols
- <leader>fS   - Workspace symbols
- <leader>fi   - Implementations
- <leader>ft   - Type definitions

## LSP Actions
- K            - Hover documentation
- <leader>rn   - Rename symbol
- <leader>ca   - Code actions
- <leader>gf   - Format code

## Diagnostics/Errors
- <leader>e    - Show diagnostic
- [d / ]d      - Previous/next diagnostic
- <leader>D    - Previous error
- <leader>d    - Next error
- <leader>q    - Diagnostic list
- <leader>wa   - All workspace diagnostics

## Git Integration
- <leader>gs   - Git status
- <leader>gb   - Git blame
- <leader>gl   - Git log

## Debugging
- <leader>dt   - Toggle breakpoint
- <leader>dc   - Continue debugging

## Quick Actions
- <leader>w    - Save file
- <leader>nh   - Clear search highlights

Advanced grep args: --type=py, --glob=*.js, --case-sensitive
EOF